    "summary": "sadhguru.org exposes 3 documented HTTP integration surfaces: Global PRS API, ISO Website integration API, and MyMedic integration API; all require auth (Bearer + x-system-token for Global PRS, OAuth2 for ISO Website and MyMedic), with no GraphQL, MCP, or CLI surfaces found.",
